This page documents the item system in Dragon Warrior IV for the NES.

==Item System Overview==

Items are indexed using 7 bits ($00-$7F). The high bit (bit 7) indicates whether an item is currently equipped.

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Property !! Value !! Description
|-
| Item ID Range || $00-$7F || 128 possible items
|-
| Equipment Range || $00-$50 || Weapons, armor, shields, helmets
|-
| Consumable Range || $52-$7E || Items used from menu
|-
| Equipped Flag || $80 || Added to ID when item is equipped
|-
| No Item || $7F || Empty slot marker
|-
| Separator || $51 || Blank/unused slot
|}

